The paper deals with the problem of phase retrieval from Fourier measurements, which is a topic in both information theory (cs.IT) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convex optimization techniques also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-category. Additionally, the use of coded diffraction patterns may suggest the paper could also belong to the signal processing (cs.SI) or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
